data.description: Highlands multi level home is looking for a new owner.  Main area has new vinyl planks throughout with vaulted ceilings, an eat in kitchen along with formal dinning and living room area.  The lower walkout level family room is perfect for friends and family gatherings,  features a fireplace and plus a half bath for easy access for your guests.  Upstairs you have 3 bedrooms, full bathroom and primary 3/4 bath.   The basement level has the utility room, storage and extra non conforming bedroom with new vinyl plank flooring.  You will love the oversized, two car garage with more storage if need be.  All of this plus,  a newly built storage shed, fenced yard, covered patio space and newer roof.
